                    <binding xml:id="binding" contemporary="true">
                        <decoNote xml:id="b1">Four Coptic chain stitches attached with bridle attachments to the wooden boards, rough-hewn boards covered with tooled leather (repaired with blue thread on spine) over decorative linen patches, headband and tailband.</decoNote>
